00:04:54.513 --> 00:04:57.933
And this is exactly what Higgins started to do.

00:04:58.793 --> 00:05:03.323
He used satellite software such as Google Earth, he would look for

00:05:03.583 --> 00:05:08.693
information hidden within the photo to try to understand more about it,

00:05:08.693 --> 00:05:14.133
he would use any publicly available information to try to find the truth.

00:05:15.103 --> 00:05:21.693
He started out by engaging with people on the comment section of the British Guardian newspaper,

00:05:22.253 --> 00:05:29.183
but before long he started a blog, and then his own company, a non-profit called Bellingcat.

00:05:30.223 --> 00:05:37.763
It started out as a niche, small hobby project, but within a few years Bellingcat

00:05:37.803 --> 00:05:43.983
became a household name in the intelligence community, and is an organisation that has

00:05:43.983 --> 00:05:49.803
been referenced by the CIA, by the British Intelligence Services, and has even been

00:05:49.813 --> 00:05:55.663
labelled a “foreign agent” by Russia, for reasons that will become clear in a minute.

00:05:57.233 --> 00:06:03.613
Along the way Bellingcat has transformed the way in which intelligence is gathered, allowing

00:06:04.003 --> 00:06:11.013
and encouraging anyone, anywhere, yes even me and you, to get involved in finding the truth.

00:06:12.143 --> 00:06:18.893
Higgins’ and Bellingcat’s first major success was in relation to the Malaysian Airlines Flight

00:06:18.903 --> 00:06:26.473
17, the aeroplane which was shot down over Ukraine on its way from Amsterdam to Kuala Lumpur.

00:06:27.683 --> 00:06:35.223
To briefly remind you of what happened, on 17th July 2014, which was actually only

00:06:35.263 --> 00:06:41.083
two days after the Bellingcat website went live, this passenger aeroplane was shot

00:06:41.113 --> 00:06:48.503
down over Eastern Ukraine, killing all 283 passengers and 15 members of the crew.

00:06:49.633 --> 00:06:54.573
The finger was quickly pointed at Russian-backed rebels in Eastern Ukraine.

00:06:55.013 --> 00:06:59.013
It’s believed that they thought they had shot a Ukrainian

00:06:59.023 --> 00:07:03.153
military plane, but accidentally shot a Malaysian plane.

00:07:03.873 --> 00:07:08.103
Although it was strongly suspected that this attack was made possible

